    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，四个参与者已经排好顺序。ConsumerBackend和ConsumerConnector在左边，ProviderConnector和ProviderBackend在右边。接下来画交互流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "ProviderBackend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对。首先ConsumerConnector向ProviderConnector发起query data offers，然后ProviderConnector返回metadata。这是发现阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "query data offers",
        "return metadata"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "发现阶段画好了。下一步是协商合约？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，ConsumerConnector发送contract request，ProviderConnector回复contract agreement。接着是获取数据：ConsumerConnector请求artifact，ProviderConnector返回access information。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "contract request",
        "contract agreement",
        "request artifact",
        "return access information"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "合约协商和访问信息获取都画完了。最后的数据传输部分怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里要分两种情况，用alt框。如果是protocol.PULL，ConsumerBackend直接向ProviderBackend请求数据并接收返回；如果是protocol.PUSH，ProviderBackend主动推送数据给ConsumerBackend，然后ConsumerBackend本地处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
